div.p:
This contract will provide for payment at 3 months, 6 months and
                    9 months, in accordance with the terms suggested in the State Department letter
                    of the 25th ultimo, as follows: 

$10,000.00 on June 15, 1925;

$5,000.00 on September 15, 1925;

$4,033.00 on December 15, 1925.
